728
01:00:07,050 --> 01:00:08,630
 Hey! You go to Haedong High, right? 

729
01:00:08,630 --> 01:00:09,850
 Hang out with us! 

730
01:00:09,850 --> 01:00:11,450
 Some group of thugs! 

731
01:00:11,450 --> 01:00:12,890
 - Do you like her? 
 - What if I do? 

732
01:00:12,890 --> 01:00:13,850
 I'll harass her. 

733
01:00:13,850 --> 01:00:16,250
 I'll buy you something prettier next time. 

734
01:00:16,250 --> 01:00:18,870
 Isn't this a pretty blatant sign? 

735
01:00:18,870 --> 01:00:21,520
 Don't you know why I'm avoiding you? 

736
01:00:21,520 --> 01:00:26,050
 You should help if you see San Ha setting the table. 

737
01:00:26,050 --> 01:00:29,420
 I wonder if it would be better for you to go with your biological dad. 

738
01:00:29,420 --> 01:00:30,700
 I'll be more mindful from now on. 

739
01:00:30,700 --> 01:00:32,600
 You should forget your mom, too. 

740
01:00:32,600 --> 01:00:34,650
 You're Mr. Yoon Jeong Jae, right? 

741
01:00:34,650 --> 01:00:36,690
 Do you remember me? 

742
01:00:37,460 --> 01:00:42,610
♫  We just believed  ♫

